#*********************************************************#
#                                                         #
#     README for BPView                                   #
#       a Web-Frontend and Configuration Tool to display  #
#       Business Processes with Icinga and Nagios         #
#                                                         #
#*********************************************************#

What is BPView?
====================

BPView is the short name for Business Process View. This Tool
for Nagios and Icinga is used to display a combination of Checks
in a Business Process.


Requirements
============

Make sure the following requirements are fulfilled:
  * Webserver (Apache)
  * Perl
  * Perl Modules:
    - CGI
    - CGI::Carp
    - CGI::Session
    - YAML::Syck
    - File::Spec
    - JSON::PP
    - LWP::UserAgent
    - HTTP::Request
    - HTTP::Request::Common
    - Data::Dumper
    - Template
    - DBI			# for MySQL
    - DBD::Pg		# for PostgreSQL
    

Installation of modules on RHEL 6:

Note: You need RHEL Server Optional channel.

# yum install httpd perl perl-CGI perl-CGI-Session perl-YAML-Syck perl-JSON perl-libwww-perl perl-Template-Toolkit perl-DBI perl-DBD-Pg

